ads/2024/01/OliviaRodrigo-Billie-Eilish-Dua-Lipa-2024-Grammys-performers.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/OliviaRodrigo-Billie-Eilish-Dua-Lipa-2024-Grammys-performers-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/OliviaRodrigo-Billie-Eilish-Dua-Lipa-2024-Grammys-performers-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/OliviaRodrigo-Billie-Eilish-Dua-Lipa-2024-Grammys-performers-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/OliviaRodrigo-Billie-Eilish-Dua-Lipa-2024-Grammys-performers-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/OliviaRodrigo-Billie-Eilish-Dua-Lipa-2024-Grammys-performers-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据宣布，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">比莉·艾利什</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olivia-rodrigo">奥利维亚·罗德里戈</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">杜阿·利帕</a>将在 2024 年格莱美<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/grammys">颁奖典礼</a>上表演。</p><p>流行艺术家是首批确认参加颁奖典礼的三位现场表演者，颁奖典礼将于 2 月 4 日（星期日）在加利福尼亚州洛杉矶的 Crypto.com Arena 举行。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/billie-eilish-at-reading-festival-setlist-photos-3489881">比莉·艾利什在雷丁节：归来的英雄巩固了节日传奇的地位</a></strong></li></ul><p>艾利什、罗德里戈和利帕<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/here-are-all-the-grammys-2024-nominations-3536101">都将角逐下个月第 66 届格莱美奖的主要奖项</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-barbie-what-was-i-made-for-3468293">“我生来是为了什么？”</a> – Eilish 为<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/barbie-review-margot-robbie-ryan-gosling-3470019"><em>芭比</em></a>原声带创作的歌曲 – 获得年度唱片、年度歌曲、最佳流行独奏表演、最佳音乐视频和最佳视觉媒体歌曲奖。她<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/labrinth">与 Labrinth</a>合作的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/labrinth-and-billie-eilish-release-song-from-euphoria-soundtrack-never-felt-so-alone-3427334">《Never Felt So Alone》</a>也获得最佳流行二重奏/团体表演提名。</p><p>罗德里戈还获得了六项提名：年度专辑（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/olivia-rodrigo-guts-album-review-vampire-3493907">《胆量》</a> ）、年度唱片（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olivia-rodirgo-shares-rock-opera-inspired-new-track-vampire-3463529">《吸血鬼》</a> ）、年度歌曲（《吸血鬼》）、最佳流行独奏表演（《吸血鬼》）、最佳流行独奏表演（《吸血鬼》）流行声乐专辑（“Guts”）和最佳摇滚歌曲（“Ballad Of A Homeschooled Girl”）。</p><p>与此同时，利帕凭借她的<em>芭比</em>单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-shares-lead-single-from-barbie-movie-dance-the-night-3448502">“Dance The Night”</a>入围两个类别：年度歌曲和最佳视觉媒体歌曲。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C2JBOcLP4EO/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.9