ent/uploads/2022/12/Elton-John-live-LA-2022-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Elton-John-live-LA-2022-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>昨晚（1 月 15 日）<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elton-john">艾尔顿·约翰 (Elton John)</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/emmys">2024 年艾美奖</a>颁奖典礼上获得雕像后，获得了 EGOT 地位。</p><p>第 75 届艾美奖颁奖典礼昨天在加利福尼亚州洛杉矶孔雀剧院举行，由演员、喜剧演员兼主持人安东尼·安德森主持。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-75th-emmy-awards-full-list-of-winners-2024-3570870">第 75 届艾美奖：查看完整获奖者名单</a></strong></li></ul><p>约翰凭借他的音乐会电影<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/elton-john-final-2022-concert-to-be-livestreamed-with-support-from-dua-lipa-and-others-3348847" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《埃尔顿·约翰现场：告别道奇体育场》</em></a>赢得了杰出综艺特别节目（现场）奖，该影片于 2022 年 11 月在<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/disney">Disney+</a>上进行了直播。该项目捕捉了这位传奇艺术家在他的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/elton-john-farewell-yellow-brick-road-footage-setlist-new-orleans-show-3142538">《告别黄砖》</a>中的最后一次北美约会<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/elton-john-farewell-yellow-brick-road-footage-setlist-new-orleans-show-3142538">路&#39;游</a>。</p><p>这位音乐家因膝盖受伤而无法参加昨晚的仪式。然而，他分享了一份关于成为 EGOT 艺术家（在职业生涯中赢得艾美奖、<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/grammys">格莱美奖</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/oscars">奥斯卡奖</a>和托尼奖的人）的荣誉的声明。</p><p>约翰说：“今晚能够加入这群才华横溢的 EGOT 获奖者，我感到非常荣幸。” “走到这一刻的旅程充满了激情、奉献精神和世界各地粉丝坚定不移的支持。”</p><p>他继续说道：“今晚证明了艺术的力量以及它给我们所有人的生活带来的欢乐。感谢所有在我职业生涯中支持我的人，我非常感激。”</p><p>据<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/tv-movies/tv-movie-news/elton-john-egot-farewell-from-dodger-stadium-2023-emmy-awards-1234947099/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《滚石》杂志报道，</em></a>约翰是继<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/john-legend">约翰·传奇 (John Legend)</a>和詹妮弗·哈德森 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jennifer-hudson">Jennifer Hudson)</a>之后，第 19 位获得 EGOT 地位的人，也是第三位获奖的流行艺术家。</p><p>这位“火箭人”偶像后来在社交媒体上分享了另一条感谢信息，写道：“我们赢得了艾美奖，我在云九！！”</p><p>他补充道：“获得这一认可证明了所有参与者的热情和奉献精神，我深表感激。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C2JUbOFCnuf/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C563.803,69.06 563.154,70.057 562.106,71.106 C561.058